title: Peterson's Gagnon Doesn't Forecast a Rate Hike in 2016 (Audio)
itunes:title: Peterson's Gagnon Doesn't Forecast a Rate Hike in 2016 (Audio)
description:
(Bloomberg) -- Taking Stock with Kathleen Hays and Pimm Fox. GUEST: FED IN FOCUS: Joseph Gagnon, a Senior Fellow at the Peterson Institute for International Economics, helped edit minutes for almost two years as a Fed economist, and will weigh in on the release of the FOMC minutes.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
